<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Reading a local txt file with predefined path...]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/viewtopic.php?t=5132&amp;p=8289#p8289"><![CDATA[
You can't read files from the user's system without the user's consent, because that would be a huge privacy and security problem. <img src="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> The user needs to explicitly &quot;share&quot; a file with your app, either by selecting it in &lt;input type=file&gt; or by dragging it to your app.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4">zcorpan</a> — Thu Mar 14, 2013 1:02 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
